We’ve all had that one wine that made you fall in love with wine right?  I’ve told this story before, but my epiphany wine was this 1997 @robertmondavi To-Kalon. I had it for the first time in the Mondavi tasting room when they just released this inaugural To-Kalon and I just fell in love with it. I had accumulated 12 bottles and enjoyed them at various times for the next 19 years. July 26th, 2019 marked the day I shared my last bottle and thought it would be my last time I got to drink one. 
/*
/* 
So to my surprise Rob @wine_lifer still had a few and shared one recently!  Still wonderful after 25 years, and brought back sweet memories! Thanks Rob for sharing this beauty! — 
/*
/*
