Grab one before it disappears! ☺️🥃 This is an excellent Anejo Tequila from TC Craft.  Also available - Blanco, Reposado, & Extra Anejo, aged 9 years! For more info clic.k on the PicoLin.k on my profile page — 
/* 
Instead of harvesting 5-7-year-old agave like the big tequila brands, TC Craft allow theirs to mature for a full 9-years. And the agave is grown without chemical pesticides or herbicides.
/* 
They bake theirs in clay ovens, slowly coaxing out the sugar in the nectar and developing flavor.
/* 
They use pure Jalisco highlands spring water and natural agave yeast instead of commercial yeast. There are no additives or fillers—just agave, spring water, and wild agave yeast.
/* 
Anejo means “aged.” To qualify as Anejo, tequila must be aged at least one year. TC Craft Anejo is aged in white oak whiskey barrels for three years. With Anejo, you’re delving into a world of smoothness and complex flavor. TC Craft is perfect for sipping neat or in tequila versions of classic cocktails such as the Manhattan and Old-Fashioned. 
/*
/* 
