A recent night out, and as you know, the night starts with champagne. Some nights start out better than others…this night it was a 95 Dom Perignon. And the 95 theme continued throughout the night. 95 Stags Leap Fay and Cask 23. And ended with a 95 Chateau Latour 1/2 btl.  Everything was drinking wonderfully, and the company - just the best! I enjoyed this special evening of 1995’s paired with delicious food from Matū in Beverly Hills, loved everything!! 🙌
